title: Hannah Elliot & Magnus Walker
description:
Hannah Elliott is an automotive journalist who covers reviews and news for Bloomberg. Magnus Walker is a famous automotive personality known for his custom vintage Porsches.

Check out Hannah's articles: https://www.bloomberg.com/authors/AR_gYx13m9A/hannah-elliott

Everything Magnus is here: http://www.magnuswalker911.com/

This show is also a video, with visual assets paired to the conversation: https://youtu.be/c1Hn6GAzerA
